title.narrative: Fiji Ministry of Agriculture Support Activity (Animal Disease and organisational Design)

description.narrative: The investment provides assistance to the Fiji Ministry of Agriculture to support implementation of the Bovine Tuberculosis Eradication Campaign (BTEC) Strategy, protecting and improving the health of economically important animals. The organisational design specialist supports the priority to maintain an effective and accountable public sector which aims to produce a high performing civil service that implements government priorities and is responsive to deliver quality services to the public.
